<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>내 버킷리스트 카드</title>
    <style>
        .card {
            width: 350px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #000 20%, #14141e 35%, #1b1844 45%);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            box-shadow: 3px 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .card h2 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 20px; border-bottom: 1px solid #444; padding-bottom: 10px; }
        ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; }

        .list-item {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .list-item:hover { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); }

        .list-item img { width: 100%; height: 120px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 5px; }
        .list-item li { font-size: 1rem; margin-top: 10px; list-style: none; }

        .badge {
            position: absolute;
            top: 5px;
            right: 5px;
            background-color: #0c075b;
            color: white;
            padding: 4px 8px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .secret-memo {
            visibility: hidden; 
            background-color: rgba(0, 238, 255, 0.9);
            color: #000;
            padding: 5px 10px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -20px;
            left: 10px;
            width: 90%;
            z-index: 20;
        }

        .list-item:hover .secret-memo {
            visibility: visible;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
    <h2>이건우 1년 계획</h2>
    <ul>
        <div class="list-item">
            <span class="badge">🎯</span>
            <img src="https://www.shutterstock.com/image-vector/stick-figure-lifting-dumbbells-illustration-260nw-2621078429.jpg" alt="운동">
            <li><b>중요한 목표</b> : 건강을 위해서 근력과 체력 키우기</li>
            <div class="secret-memo">참고 : 5년간 17X에 최소49~최대52정도 유지하고 있음</div>
        </div>

        <div class="list-item">
            <span class="badge">📚</span>
            <img src="https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTPwx5Lx7ZMVyq6vGxPpDaZG-gicr5jEF3eBg&s" alt="생각">
            <li><b>2순위</b> : 3DS Max, Java, Visual studio등을 자주 이용하면서 앞으로 있을 시험에 대비하기</li>
            <div class="secret-memo">진로를 위해서라면...?</div>
        </div>

        <div class="list-item">
            <span class="badge">💰</span>
            <img src="https://previews.123rf.com/images/tribalium123/tribalium1231208/tribalium123120800408/14992885-money-in-the-hand-hand-with-money-hand-holding-banknotes.jpg" alt="절약">
            <li><b>가벼운 목표</b> : 뭐든간에 최대한 절약하기</li>
            <div class="secret-memo">이유는 당연하게도 요즘은 물가가 높아서</div>
        </div>
    </ul>
</div>

</body>
</html>
